Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> program
Rule 1     program -> program statement
Rule 2     program -> statement
Rule 3     statement -> assignment
Rule 4     assignment -> ID POW_ASSIGN expression
Rule 5     assignment -> ID INT_DIV_ASSIGN expression
Rule 6     assignment -> ID ASSIGN expression
Rule 7     expression -> INT
Rule 8     expression -> ID

