Parsing method: LALR

state 0

    (0) S' -> . program
    (1) program -> . program statement
    (2) program -> . statement
    (3) statement -> . assignment
    (4) assignment -> . ID POW_ASSIGN expression
    (5) assignment -> . ID INT_DIV_ASSIGN expression
    (6) assignment -> . ID ASSIGN expression

    ID              shift and go to state 4

    program                        shift and go to state 1
    statement                      shift and go to state 2
    assignment                     shift and go to state 3

state 1

    (0) S' -> program .
    (1) program -> program . statement
    (3) statement -> . assignment
    (4) assignment -> . ID POW_ASSIGN expression
    (5) assignment -> . ID INT_DIV_ASSIGN expression
    (6) assignment -> . ID ASSIGN expression

    ID              shift and go to state 4

    statement                      shift and go to state 5
    assignment                     shift and go to state 3

state 2

    (2) program -> statement .

    ID              reduce using rule 2 (program -> statement .)
    $end            reduce using rule 2 (program -> statement .)


state 3

    (3) statement -> assignment .

    ID              reduce using rule 3 (statement -> assignment .)
    $end            reduce using rule 3 (statement -> assignment .)


state 4

    (4) assignment -> ID . POW_ASSIGN expression
    (5) assignment -> ID . INT_DIV_ASSIGN expression
    (6) assignment -> ID . ASSIGN expression

    POW_ASSIGN      shift and go to state 6
    INT_DIV_ASSIGN  shift and go to state 7
    ASSIGN          shift and go to state 8


state 5

    (1) program -> program statement .

    ID              reduce using rule 1 (program -> program statement .)
    $end            reduce using rule 1 (program -> program statement .)


state 6

    (4) assignment -> ID POW_ASSIGN . expression
    (7) expression -> . INT
    (8) expression -> . ID

    INT             shift and go to state 11
    ID              shift and go to state 9

    expression                     shift and go to state 10

state 7

    (5) assignment -> ID INT_DIV_ASSIGN . expression
    (7) expression -> . INT
    (8) expression -> . ID

    INT             shift and go to state 11
    ID              shift and go to state 9

    expression                     shift and go to state 12

state 8

    (6) assignment -> ID ASSIGN . expression
    (7) expression -> . INT
    (8) expression -> . ID

    INT             shift and go to state 11
    ID              shift and go to state 9

    expression                     shift and go to state 13

state 9

    (8) expression -> ID .

    ID              reduce using rule 8 (expression -> ID .)
    $end            reduce using rule 8 (expression -> ID .)


state 10

    (4) assignment -> ID POW_ASSIGN expression .

    ID              reduce using rule 4 (assignment -> ID POW_ASSIGN expression .)
    $end            reduce using rule 4 (assignment -> ID POW_ASSIGN expression .)


state 11

    (7) expression -> INT .

    ID              reduce using rule 7 (expression -> INT .)
    $end            reduce using rule 7 (expression -> INT .)


state 12

    (5) assignment -> ID INT_DIV_ASSIGN expression .

    ID              reduce using rule 5 (assignment -> ID INT_DIV_ASSIGN expression .)
    $end            reduce using rule 5 (assignment -> ID INT_DIV_ASSIGN expression .)


state 13

    (6) assignment -> ID ASSIGN expression .

    ID              reduce using rule 6 (assignment -> ID ASSIGN expression .)
    $end            reduce using rule 6 (assignment -> ID ASSIGN expression .)

